{"tid":702379,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細扣起例假話跟銀行假","createTime":"2018-06-15T00:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T04:58:33.000Z","uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9cc3b914dfc99b3f533af4a59c82b28885461c","tid":702379,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:28:13.000Z","msg":"咁我地本身返5.5（星期日休息）<br />\n如果果個星期有紅日撞左要返工既日子就冇例假<br />\n比如下星期端午節 咁下星期就冇例假放<br />\n有個同事做多四年<br />\n但佢一年半前先突然話有呢條政策 係跟銀行假放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老細可能覺得請多左人 開支大左<br />\n如果fulltime放例假 就要請parttime頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd956bbc95a659b411c47d4fe5f0f05f842fedf7","tid":702379,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"即係紅日放假 例假要番？<br />\n咁你夠唔夠每七日一個休息日？"},{"pid":"2117098335a79b2726bcee6d2319ffcb9f201023","tid":702379,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:48:14.000Z","msg":"屌你up乜春<br />\n即係端午個星期要返埋星前日？"},{"pid":"39f7fd1707988e559ba2a7c1042f37124c37ca4a","tid":702379,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"跟銀行?<br />\n銀行星期日唔開喎<br />\n你問下你老闆仲跟唔跟銀行"},{"pid":"2eb96eeda36f1f4a10e06507643e3eb7c81b0874","tid":702379,"uid":102196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:51:25.000Z","msg":"法定假期唔可以當例假，去勞工處告佢啦"},{"pid":"95b4e5b4ab61df1b2a2b6df099f04862227d013c","tid":702379,"uid":18021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 組織好先再講"},{"pid":"8a95bdf4c120eb54c5ed13c43dbda395471592c7","tid":702379,"uid":102196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57f_whole.htm&d=4QFUcMGHpN3Zj9TGzmZjhh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=e18b6af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57f_whole.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n問5.\t如果法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主是否須要另外補假？<br />\n答5.\t<br />\n須要。如法定假日適逢僱員的休息日，僱主應於休息日翌日補假。該補假須並非法定假日，另定假日，代替假日或休息日的日子。"},{"pid":"b41b102bc0e732502064a38e6fe00d6c4f449e3d","tid":702379,"uid":22481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:54:03.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"9ce57802f9e48f7264148f55e9aa342ef8c4ed56","tid":702379,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b4e5b4ab61df1b2a2b6df099f04862227d013c","tid":702379,"uid":18021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 組織好先再講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"相信樓主同老細商量時都1999先奶晒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f96e8571e6016d62f36c7b1369a1b0097a55cee","tid":702379,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"你做庇護工場嫁？"},{"pid":"77b09f1aed53e40f12812858aed9f0de3d9a39e8","tid":702379,"uid":22622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"你串返佢咩係銀行假，香港得公眾假期同埋勞工假期<br />\n<br />\n再屌佢老母端午節係勞工假黎，要你返工就要擇日補返一日假俾你"},{"pid":"da3d2b1ab79ba4088536b445d8621b9036f60288","tid":702379,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd956bbc95a659b411c47d4fe5f0f05f842fedf7","tid":702379,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"即係紅日放假 例假要番？<br />\n咁你夠唔夠每七日一個休息日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n都夠 逢星期日休一日"},{"pid":"9e9dab4ec143ebe9561f525af536880737722261","tid":702379,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"Sor 搭搭下車諗到開post 未訓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.